Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:10.67,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反应弹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.76,0:11:13.37,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有这玩意儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.44,0:11:23.81,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全体天顶星人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.27,0:11:27.49,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说这颗星球上沉睡着了不得的宝藏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.74,0:11:29.02,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有飞船和它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.05,0:11:30.58,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.66,0:11:34.36,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小人们出现前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.68,0:11:37.15,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙的支配者是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.57,0:11:39.54,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗 掠夺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.71,0:11:42.21,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重现我们当年的荣光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.50,0:11:50.09,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天顶星 天顶星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:54.73,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:11:59.36,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你啊 计划还算顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.80,0:12:01.67,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.71,0:12:33.67,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似反应弹的保管库被打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.95,0:12:50.75,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别上蹿下跳的 小人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.49,0:12:56.97,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SMS的机体被…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.05,0:12:59.87,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掩护 允许开火
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.04,0:13:03.82,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开干了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.41,0:13:05.21,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:11.79,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反应弹的搭载呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.79,0:13:12.57,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:14.54,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时待命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:18.13,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们一开始就这打算
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.80,0:13:20.25,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 小人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:22.42,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱首歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:25.78,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定能阻止我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.93,0:13:41.19,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再耽误了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.62,0:13:42.88,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射舰炮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.27,0:13:52.52,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰桥听令 舰炮准备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.65,0:13:55.68,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:03.66,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多 有你的生日礼物快递
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.19,0:14:12.29,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 拥抱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.75,0:14:14.61,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到银河的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.35,0:14:29.54,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.43,0:14:51.14,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.40,0:14:53.14,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.88,0:14:56.68,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是把握代演机会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.69,0:14:58.44,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踏上巨星之路的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.03,0:15:01.98,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超时空灰姑娘！兰歌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.97,0:15:07.14,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:11.42,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为肯定赶不上演唱会了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.54,0:15:57.54,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.51,0:16:11.42,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 混账
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:22.08,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.46,0:16:34.09,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:45.68,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群蠢货 被轻易驯服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.77,0:16:56.48,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要除掉她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.52,0:16:59.95,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:04.71,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死心吧 你败了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.84,0:17:05.81,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:08.07,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许对我发号施令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.67,0:17:16.72,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:17.63,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌声？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.71,0:17:19.87,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逗人笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.12,0:17:22.68,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗才是我们天顶星人的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:24.91,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的血液
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.80,0:17:28.46,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继承着血液
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.09,0:17:31.42,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近似于诅咒的演绎者之血
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.06,0:17:38.30,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就是为此而被制造的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.68,0:17:41.31,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能以此为生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.53,0:17:50.58,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么演绎者之血
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.99,0:17:53.91,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.76,0:17:56.28,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:12.81,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我记住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.50,0:18:15.46,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙再大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:18.66,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也容不下两个种类的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:37.88,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起啊 这姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:07.44,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疯了吗你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.47,0:19:10.80,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞行服都不穿 血肉之躯上战场来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.32,0:19:13.25,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.81,0:19:16.90,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也许不会投入听…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.46,0:19:23.00,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为什么 一放松腿就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:26.34,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌 你到底为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.48,0:19:29.75,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为想亲口传达
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:34.61,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快乐 阿鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.95,0:19:55.19,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.73,0:19:58.63,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想永远这样飞下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.06,0:20:00.95,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:07.49,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,返程交给你了 阿鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:09.61,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.87,0:20:12.07,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌的首演是明天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:14.71,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要用上它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.85,0:20:20.34,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.46,0:20:22.43,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢丽尔有我带回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:23.72,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.46,0:20:28.91,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体谅下兰歌冒险来这里的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.73,0:20:34.32,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…兰歌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.37,0:20:36.41,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.01,0:20:39.28,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么好感谢的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.66,0:20:42.07,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我自己想来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.61,0:20:45.08,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过多亏你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.74,0:20:48.58,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最棒的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.81,0:21:13.06,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:29.13,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.86,0:21:30.96,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操纵…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.56,0:21:44.65,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.36,0:21:56.15,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.90,0:22:07.61,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.30,0:22:10.17,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.62,0:22:15.73,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.84,0:22:21.04,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Macross
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.61,0:23:55.82,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然出现的第一代Macross舰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.21,0:23:58.23,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其雄姿再现时
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.38,0:24:01.00,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多见证了星球的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.61,0:24:03.62,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 Memory of Global
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.90,0:24:06.16,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激扬的歌声 响彻银河
